  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>KIM SENG HUAT HARDWARE PTE LTD is the leading supplier and distributor of piping system components to the Energy, Marine, Water infrastructure and other industries in Southeast Asia.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>This role supports sales, purchasing, and administrative functions by assisting procurement, coordinating shipments, and ensuring timely deliveries within the Sales Department.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in managing daily procurement tasks to ensure timely ordering and supply of materials</li><li>Prepare purchase quotations and follow up with vendors to confirm delivery schedules</li><li>Coordinate and consolidate shipments to optimize delivery efficiency for the Sales Department</li><li>Collaborate effectively with colleagues to meet on-time delivery targets</li><li>Participate in stock take exercises to maintain accurate inventory records</li><li>Perform additional duties as assigned by supervisors to support department operations</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Proficient in using MS Office applications (Word, Excel, PowerPoint) to prepare documents and reports</li><li>Communicate clearly in written and spoken English and Mandarin to liaise with Mandarin-speaking vendors</li><li>Demonstrate attention to detail and take initiative in completing tasks accurately</li><li>Organize work proactively and collaborate well within a team environment with minimal supervision</li><li>Willingness to work at the Jurong location</li></ul>",
